tags: i dont actually hate tonks and remus
body:
Remus Lupin’s true biography

Remus John Lupin was bitten young and now turned into a scary monster every month. He went to Hogwarts as all young wizards do and fell in love with Sirius black. After the death of James and Lilly Potter he was alone and in poverty. And then his true love Sirius Black escaped Azkaban and they lived together for some time. Two years after Sirius and Remus were reunited, Sirius was caught up in a battle in the Ministry of magic and fell through a portal where he landed in a nice town to stay in for a few years. Alive. Bitch.

Anyway, Remus was best friends with the very gay nymphadora tonks who he accidentally put a baby into somehow. So they got married to raise the baby as besties. They both fought in the battle of Hogwarts too, and halfway through decided to take a nice nap in the middle of the great Hall. After the battle Remus found Sirius in the town and they lived happily ever after. Also tonks found a girlfriend.
